{"tid":536724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不吃不喝19年】調查指香港連續8年 成全球樓價最難負擔城市","createTime":"2018-01-22T05:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T06:49:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed36db531161011144866db118f0bc5837d370a","tid":536724,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"國際機構Demographia發表2017年國際樓價負擔能力報告，香港連續8年成為最難負擔城市，樓價對比收入比率，由2016年的18.1倍升至19.4倍，即一般家庭不吃不喝19.4年才買到樓，19.4亦創調查報告新高，顯示香港樓價負擔情況進一步惡化。<br />\n<br />\n香港負擔比率為19.4，遠遠拋離第2位澳洲悉尼的12.9及第3位加拿大溫哥華的12.6。第4位是美國加州聖荷西San Jose，報10.3，第5位是澳洲墨爾本，達9.9。<br />\n<br />\n調查表二，有28個城市的樓價難以令人負擔，其中澳洲5個、新西蘭1個、中國1個、加拿大2個、美國13個及英國6個。<br />\n<br />\n調查對像包括中國、美國、澳洲、英國、加拿大、新加坡、日本、新西蘭、愛爾蘭等，合共293個城市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180122/57739321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180122%2F57739321&d=2sqDBBqJzP5ZBWXjfw5LSZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=94fd52a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180122%2F57739321&h=eae42859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180122/57739321</a>"},{"pid":"9ce78bee427530cd1f08946e1101474de93f4ba2","tid":536724,"uid":131731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"咩最高樓價啊, 最大壓力啊, 最高工時啊就肯撚定係香港<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"6b8bce7905dc9298e8bf78240a2084134bb6802c","tid":536724,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:42:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc570332d066680f6fd2b3b7ae61552b387ad105","tid":536724,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61637e4e6f3312f639ba4e27da5808bc9e2586ca","tid":536724,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce78bee427530cd1f08946e1101474de93f4ba2","tid":536724,"uid":131731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"咩最高樓價啊, 最大壓力啊, 最高工時啊就肯撚定係香港<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"你睇下D新樓閒閒地2,3千萬起跳, 都唔洗講豪宅區5,6千萬起跳嗰D<br />\n冇香港奴工咩都高就係要求低既性格, 班老闆點買咁多靚車靚樓呀"},{"pid":"83a49257493678628f410c0213a5a5769e7a06cc","tid":536724,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"有冇圖表"},{"pid":"04a2db2b0b07d21b14159a478e826fb84398b2c2","tid":536724,"uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"83a49257493678628f410c0213a5a5769e7a06cc","tid":536724,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"有冇圖表"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/22/144709_cdcc13c6314900d7b5d0ddeae2ff32f6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F144709_cdcc13c6314900d7b5d0ddeae2ff32f6.png&h=a952461a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://demographia.com/dhi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdemographia.com%2Fdhi.pdf&d=2sqDBBqJzP5ZBWXjfw5LSZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=02b44df0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://demographia.com/dhi.pdf</a>"}]}